---
title: Greek-Style Chicken & Fresh Veggie Couscous with Garlic Yoghurt
description: Chicken and veggies can get a little tiresome, but we bet with this new twist, everyone at the table will be wanting a second
helping. A cooling, garlic infused yoghurt sits dolloped on top of an array of veggies and couscous for that touch of tang - it can be confirmed that chicken and veggies are back in the good books!

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*

